{"tid":1332550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【強烈譴責別有用心人士偽冒學生動源發佈假消息】","createTime":"2019-07-19T10:35:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T10:50:38.000Z","uid":153615,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"85fb47bcd414ee41dc9444c99902bca717a00f00","tid":1332550,"uid":153615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T10:35:41.000Z","msg":"本日下午時份，Telegram各群組流傳以下圖片聲稱學生動源呼籲721當日各區市民到各自地區「遍地開花」，對此學生動源嚴正澄清，本組織絕無公開作出任何呼籲，所有學生動源資訊以學生動源Facebook 專頁、Instagram Page 、Telegram 公告頻道、Twitter Page為凖。<br />\n<br />\n學生動源對近日多宗涉及本組織的假資訊事件作出強烈譴責，學生動源相信有關行為旨在誤導市民以及令本組織聲譽受損，本組織呼籲別有居心人士停止有關行為。<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月19日<br />\n學生動源<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n【學生動源Facebook專頁】<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/studentlocalism/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstudentlocalism%2F&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=c43c3f00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/studentlocalism/</a><br />\n<br />\n【學生動源Instagram專頁】<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/studentlocalism/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fstudentlocalism%2F&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=a759b4ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/studentlocalism/</a><br />\n<br />\n【學生動源Twitter專頁】：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/studentlocalism\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstudentlocalism&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=dc4d3922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/studentlocalism</a><br />\n<br />\n【學生動源Telegram公告頻道】：<a href=\"https://t.me/studentlocalism\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstudentlocalism&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=345ab6ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/studentlocalism</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/76YvhN2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt